channel.title: Half-assed 481 Cleanup
channel.description: I've spent the last day or so cleaning a 481 deob. It's nowhere near even halfway finished, but I'd like to post it before a RS update makes it obsolete. Also, if anyone would be kind enough to do so, suggest a better name for SomeListShit. It's just not a very descriptive name. http://s1.uppit.com/d/U43R1A Also, not all unrenamed classes are uncleaned. I didn't take the better part of half a day to rename and clean ten classes or however many there are.

item.title: Half-assed 481 Cleanup
item.dc:creator: @Silver_Lining Silver Lining
item.description:
@Silver_Lining wrote:

Really, I don’t care if it’s begging for some pattern to be broken. Chances are, most little fucks who rely on others to figure out what anything in the client really is won’t have any idea what my mnemonics translate to in their own naming, so I’m not worried about this being informative either. It’s mainly to show how beautiful the client is after you’ve removed all the ugly shit from obfuscation and decompiling.
